00:38:11.127 --> 00:38:14.457
And what you're doing
is you're trying to find it.

598
00:38:14.627 --> 00:38:17.287
- Reveal it. All right?
- Okay.

599
00:38:17.727 --> 00:38:21.167
Every carve counts.
Why are you smiling? Don't smile.

600
00:38:21.337 --> 00:38:25.327
- I'm not smiling. I'm excited.
- This isn't like hacking a piece of ice.

