00:38:35.017 --> 00:38:38.007
- Here we go.
- What are you doing?

605
00:38:39.357 --> 00:38:41.407
If you're gonna do it, do it right.

606
00:38:41.587 --> 00:38:44.747
All right, look.
First of all, with the grain.

607
00:38:44.987 --> 00:38:48.017
With the grain.
You see what I'm doing here?

608
00:38:48.257 --> 00:38:52.027
You let the tool do the work.
You see?

609
00:38:52.197 --> 00:38:55.027
Just like you're riding a wave.
You let the wave do the work.

610
00:38:55.197 --> 00:38:59.397
