629
00:39:59.166 --> 00:40:00.496
I don't want your help.

630
00:40:00.666 --> 00:40:02.666
- You don't want my help?
- I don't want your help.

631
00:40:02.806 --> 00:40:05.866
- All right. Fine.
- I want to make my board.

632
00:40:06.036 --> 00:40:09.596
